==語源==
「-{耶利哥}-」的名字無論是從希伯來語還是現代阿拉伯語<ref name=Schreiberp141>Schreiber, 2003, p. 141.</ref><ref name=Ringp367>Ring et al., 1994, [https://books.google.com/books?id=R44VRnNCzAYC&pg=RA1-PA367&dq=jericho+babylonian+ring&lr=#v=onepage&q=&f=false p. 367–370] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=R44VRnNCzAYC&pg=RA1-PA367&dq=jericho+babylonian+ring&lr=#v=onepage&q=&f=false |date=20190609083216 }}.</ref><ref name=Bromileyp1136>Bromiley, 1995, p. 1136.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://faculty.gordon.edu/hu/bi/Ted_Hildebrandt/OTeSources/01-Genesis/Text/Articles-Books/Waltke_CreationIV_BSac.pdf|title=Bibliotheca Sacra 132|year=1975|pages=327–42|access-date=2017-02-23|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118231611/http://faculty.gordon.edu/hu/bi/ted_hildebrandt/OTeSources/01-Genesis/Text/Articles-Books/Waltke_CreationIV_BSac.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，一樣源於[[迦南語|迦南語]]的「''Reaẖ''」，意思就是「香氛」。

不過，亦有意見認為這個名字其實應該是原於迦南語的另一個字「''Yareaẖ''」，意思就是「[[月亮|月亮]]」或「[[月神#女神|月神]]」，而歷史學家亦已知道古時當地是月神信仰的中心<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.htmlbible.com/sacrednamebiblecom/kjvstrongs/STRHEB34.htm |title=Strong's Bible Dictionary |publisher=Htmlbible.com |date= |accessdate=2011-03-31 |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916032031/http://www.htmlbible.com/sacrednamebiblecom/kjvstrongs/STRHEB34.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

